import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import Avatar from './Avatar'

const layoutProps = {
  
};
export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}>

<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"avatars"}}>{`Avatars`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`Avatars`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"properties"}}>{`Properties`}</MDXTag>
<PropsTable of={Avatar} />
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"example"}}>{`Example`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __codesandbox={`undefined`} __position={1} __code={'<Avatar size=\"xxl\" online={true} />\n<Avatar size=\"xl\" shape=\"rounded\" />\n<Avatar size=\"lg\" />\n<Avatar online={true} shape=\"rounded\" />\n<Avatar size=\"sm\" online={false} />\n<Avatar size=\"xs\" />'} __scope={{props: this ? this.props : props,Avatar}}>
    <Avatar size="xxl" online={true} />
    <Avatar size="xl" shape="rounded" />
    <Avatar size="lg" />
    <Avatar online={true} shape="rounded" />
    <Avatar size="sm" online={false} />
    <Avatar size="xs" />
</Playground>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
